playerinfo.autoalliance.Birdsong=1st: Reveal an order card.<br><br>2nd: Craft order card for <style="vpone">1</style> if it has an available item.<br><br>3rd: Revolt<br>Remove all enemy pieces from the ordered sympathetic clearing with the most enemy pieces, and place the ordered base there. If the order cards is a <sprite name="birdicon">, do this in daylight instead. <br><br>4th: Public Pity<br>If you did not revolt this turn, spread sympathy twice if you have four or fewer sympathetic clearings, or spread sympathy once if you have five or more.
playerinfo.autoalliance.daylight=1st: Spread Sympathy<br>Place a sympathy token in the ordered clearing with the fewest enemy warriors adjacent to any sympathetic clearing. If you have no such clearing, instead place sympathy in the clearing with the fewest enemy pieces. If you can't place a sympathy token, gain <style="vpnum">5 . <br><br>2nd: Surprise Revolt<br>If the order card is a <sprite name="birdicon">, revolt in a clearing matching the suit of an unused base.
playerinfo.autoalliance.evening=1st: Organize<br>In each clearing with a base and three or more Alliance warriors, remove all Alliance warriors there and spread sympathy.<br><br>2nd: Recruit<br>Place a warrior in each clearing with a base.
